content.description: Located about 1/2 mile west of the end loop past Moosedog. Walk for about 1/2 hour to obvious largest dark buttress, seen as you approach. The climb goes past a few bolts, then up cracks to a sling anchor on a tied off section of rock. The climb faces North.
content.protection: A rack of trad gear, mostly small to med.
content.location: SW of the end of the road past Moosedog Tower, Indian Cove Campground.

climbs.name: Erotic Driving
climbs.fa: Todd Gordon, Tucker Tech, Beth Shilliday,

content.description: This interesting route takes a line up a large wall, just left of Kentucky Waterfall. Follow bolts up a featured face until a hand crack is reached. The final moves surmount a summit cap by an O W crack. Anchor on top. This climb is mostly 5.10- , with one 5.11 move, past a bolt. From the end loop past Moosedog, hike about 10 min. and look up and south. Erotic Driving goes up the face just left of the huge roof. There are two crack to the left of this;..the one just left has been done at 5.8, and the one left of that was soloed (5.6)
content.protection: Bolts for the face section, and hands to bigger for the crack section.
content.location: SW of the end of the road past Moosedog Tower.
